Hi <%= @user.username %>,

thanks for signing up! This email is just a note to let you know that
your account has been successfully created.

<% unless @user.activated? -%>
Your account will have to be approved by a moderator before you'll be able
to access the site. We'll drop you a new note once your approval
status changes.

<% end -%>
<% if @user.openid_url? -%>
You've signed up using your OpenID URL:

  <%= @user.openid_url %>
<% elsif @user.facebook? -%>
You've signed up using your Facebook account.
<% end -%>

You can log in here:
<%= @login_url %>

Have fun!
